U.S. August Primary Metals Leading Index: Summary

-- B y   M i k e   S e b a n y
-- 
2011-09-16T14:00:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/u-s-august-primary-metals-leading-index-summary-table-.html
The U.S. primary metals leading
index fell in August, according to the  U.S. Geological Survey .  The index, a gauge of industry activity over the next eight
months, fell 1.5 percent following a 0.5 percent drop in July.  
